{"tid":2334044,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"見你地係咁抽阿記水，真係好唔開心","createTime":"2020-12-21T01:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T13:50:16.000Z","uid":13395,"like":6,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"95bd9418cd7063bc258244e38547b465a82be21a","tid":2334044,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:49:10.000Z","msg":"見到你地係咁抽阿記水<br />\n我真係越諗越撚灰<br />\n根本唔知自己做乜要支持一隊球隊10幾年而換得俾人嘲笑既地步<br />\n知唔知咩叫尊重、respect?<br />\n好撚煩囉成日搬D歷史出o黎話點話點<br />\n我心諗一句, 你講既我全部知, 甚至乎你唔知既我都知<br />\n第一唔使你教我<br />\n第二唔使你分析我聽<br />\n第三我無屌你隊愛隊先<br />\n一失分出面最少半版post 係抽水<br />\n好難忍到一個都唔reply<br />\n或者轉去其他forum 係唯一解決方法"},{"pid":"7422a4d9ff8aeb7e6ad05fb06c9255ddc3329533","tid":2334044,"uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"琴晚見白禮頓絕殺唔到幾失望"},{"pid":"6678bbe3292718298df777ba5a08c7671febcfe2","tid":2334044,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:51:22.000Z","msg":"支持樓主轉forum🙏🏻💪🏻"},{"pid":"6b82f3d0d164ee4d26931e7e8496a19fd12e874e","tid":2334044,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:53:25.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88897114434435e2b954ce9486126fdcb142c455","tid":2334044,"uid":317485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:54:58.000Z","msg":"回家吧！ 阿joe的大門還開着<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc326e431d00db94af0a6ee23514d1bf1f069fdf","tid":2334044,"uid":63253,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:58:27.000Z","msg":"阿迷最識尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5d36ea82c92061a336d34f2f8ced375a289f40","tid":2334044,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88897114434435e2b954ce9486126fdcb142c455","tid":2334044,"uid":317485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T01:54:58.000Z","msg":"回家吧！ 阿